<subsection xml:id="subsec-Division-of-a-fraction-by-a-whole-number">
        <title>Division of a fraction by a whole number</title>
        <activity>
            <statement>
                <p>
                   <alert>Work in groups</alert>
                </p>
                <p>
                    Mr. Obiero is a meat seller in Namanga center.He always ensure food safety and hygiene when handling and selling meat.
                     He is selling <m>\frac{1}{2}</m> kg of meat to four teachers of Seku primary school.
                </p>
                <p>
                    <ol marker="a)">
                        <li>
                            <p>  
                               1. What fraction of the meat will each teacher receive if they share it equally?
                            </p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p>
                               2. Share your answer with other learners in your class.
                            </p>
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                </p>
            </statement>
        </activity>
        <p>
            When dividing a fraction by a whole number, multiply the fraction by the reciprocal of the whole.
        </p>
        <example>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    Work out: <m>\frac{3}{20} \div 6  </m>
                </p>
            </statement>
            <solution>
                <p>
                    <ol marker="a)">
                        <li>
                            <p>
                                Find the reciprocal of the divisor.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                The reciprocal of <m>6</m> is <m>\frac{1}{6}.</m>
                            </p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p>
                                Multiply.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                <md>
                                    <mrow>\frac{3}{20} \times \frac{1}{6} \amp = \frac{3 \times 1}{20 \times 6}</mrow>
                                    <mrow></mrow>
                                    <mrow> \amp = \frac{3}{120} </mrow>
                                    <mrow></mrow>
                                    <mrow> \frac{3}{120} \amp = \frac{3 \div 3}{120 \div 3} </mrow>
                                    <mrow></mrow>
                                    <mrow> \amp = \frac{1}{40}</mrow>
                                </md>
                            </p>
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                </p>
            </solution>
        </example>
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    Exercise for Division of a fraction by a whole number
                </p>
            </statement>
        </exercise>
    </subsection>